"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Just for reference, Activision Blizzard holds what is probably the best gaming portfolio in the world - Warcraft, Diablo, Overwatch, Call of Duty, Candy Crush \\n  \\n The move is being touted to boost the portfolio of different games under their Xbox Game Pass service \\n  \\n Okay, if we look at it from a theoretical point of view, a pass that allows the user to enter different gaming worlds, have a unique experience and leave at any time (hop-in, hop-out) \\n  \\n Sounds very close to the bird's eye vision of what Zuck highlighted at FB Connect 2021 \\n  \\n Interesting to see two giants approaching the same concept from two different strategies - Top-to-bottom (FB), Bottom-up (Microsoft) \\n  \\n ... and, in-turn how this plays out in their corporate strategy is quite interesting! \\n  \\n Since FB is taking a top-to-bottom approach, most of the focus will be on the development of tools for allowing creators to build these different worlds, and hence, we can see that play out in their hiring strategy and their plan to hire >10,000 developers for the metaverse team \\n  \\n On the flip side, Microsoft has gone on an acquisition spree (Minecraft, Bethesda ... and now Activision Blizzard), bringing the currently disjointed worlds together, and hence the corporate strategy focuses on M&A, over, building \\n  \\n Two different approaches, will one win, or will they be more collaborative this time around (a gamer can hope!)?\",\"timestamp\":1642561229,\"title\":\"Microsoft just announced their acquisition of one of the biggest gaming studios in the world for a whopping ~ $69 Billion\"},\"digest\":\"Lj_gwRO-kGVne6SJTIVV5QLB3bwuKO2xVceoeWOZMXA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF41DF18b77bec4e196Ecf0178820313F9Fca3562\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"U_dKQ2RMVBV129-Evi0zS2AAC6judCAJk_AFL2lcPVU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IecgH4Q-DTv8_7teMlBmEVN00_kIrR8Dh6xPFcKFj0s\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"W360j11Rv8CDRHYLkqOPni9Alt4U2UIMvnx1RKN0uLUCyop0XTKZKoPtZaU7ORCwjUyZardIQTpL4wj25repQA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xcb9888152117ca560f964a6878a716d8c47db0562c7d3c39916735bb3433a5252b26ec947ff4d8899a458e084740fca958e8f4f6d0cf6c90547cdb29dc154e1f1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"U_dKQ2RMVBV129-Evi0zS2AAC6judCAJk_AFL2lcPVU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IecgH4Q-DTv8_7teMlBmEVN00_kIrR8Dh6xPFcKFj0s\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Lj_gwRO-kGVne6SJTIVV5QLB3bwuKO2xVceoeWOZMXA\"}"